channel.title: Introducing Kollege.co Learn to code
channel.description:
Hi there,
I have been a big fan of Bootstrapped.fm over the years but haven't had an opportunity to post anything but today I finished my project to help people learn to code.
I would love your feedback and it would be cool to know if anyone would be interested in using such a service.
Kollege.co
Thank you
